{"type": "article", "id": 27667, "title": "可折叠座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-02T07:27:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135029A6d9zFZoeYPtMpbR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这款非常吸睛的可折叠座椅 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rest/rest-the-worlds-most-compact-foldable-seat\">Sitpack</a> 可以说是新的排队神器，替人们解决了在外无处休息的难题，缓解疲惫。它的顶部是两瓣可以折叠起来的座椅，合起来的时候就成了一个包装盒，能够容纳下方的椅腿。伸缩后 Sitpack 的大小也就相当于一个啤酒罐，仅重 0.56 千克，便于随身携带。Sitpack 底部的圆形橡胶垫能够牢牢的抓住地面保证安全，最多可以承受 100 千克的重量。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.sitpack.dk/home/8-sitpack.html\">购买链接</a>，售价为 60 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135026mn5W26Vd8TqH7zhF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135027xLsIg9J6hn2NVSUC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213502705YH9MsBOvS84Dya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135028sX0iDHwgVJb1lENp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}